;; ESCíê¶ 2è¸°ë‰ì‘æ¿¡œ æ¹²ê³—ã€ˆìë¿‰ 3è¸°ˆ ESCç‘œ¼ ëë‹ƒëìœ­ìë¹ ìì˜‰ëë£íë¸¯ëëœ• escapeç‘œ¼ ëŒ€ìë–Šíë¹€ëë•²ëë–
(global-set-key (kbd "<escape> <escape>") 'keyboard-escape-quit)

;; C-x C-z íê¶åª›€ suspend-frameìì‘æ¿¡œ ëë¦ºìë¼±ìì—³ìë¼±ìê½Œ ìì˜’ï§ì‚µë¹ìê½Œ emacsåª›€ ï§ë‰í…›ëë’— å¯ƒìŒìŠ¦åª›€ ìê¹®æ¹²ê³•¯€æ¿¡œ íë¹ìì £íë¹€ëë•²ëë–
(global-unset-key (kbd "C-x C-z"))

;; White spaceç‘œ¼ ìë¾¾ìë¸·äºŒì‡°ë’— íë¸¿ìë‹”
(defun kill-whitespace ()
  "Kill the whitespace between two non-whitespace characters"
  (interactive "*")
  (save-excursion
    (save-restriction
      (save-match-data
        (progn
          (re-search-forward "[ \t\r\n]+" nil t)
          (replace-match "" nil nil))))))

;; Alt + w íê¶æ¿¡œ white-spaceç‘œ¼ ìì £å«„ê³ ë¸¯ëë’— æ¹²ê³•ë’«ìì“£ ìê½•ìì ™íë¹€ëë•²ëë–
(global-set-key (kbd "M-w") 'kill-whitespace)
(define-key c++-mode-map (kbd "M-w") 'kill-whitespace)

;; Alt + m íê¶æ¿¡œ æ€¨ë“¬ê°šëë±¾ìì“£ ìì £å«„ê³ ë¹€ëë•²ëë–
(global-set-key (kbd "M-m") 'delete-blank-lines)

;; Alt + f íê¶æ¿¡œ forward paragraph (C-<down>) æ€¨¼ åª›ìˆˆ€ ï§ë‚…ì¡Šìì“£ ìë–íë»¾íë¹€ëë•²ëë–
(global-set-key (kbd "M-f") 'forward-paragraph)
(define-key c++-mode-map (kbd "M-f") 'forward-paragraph)

;; Alt + r íê¶æ¿¡œ backward paragraph (C-<up>) æ€¨¼ åª›ìˆˆ€ ï§ë‚…ì¡Šìì“£ ìë–íë»¾íë¹€ëë•²ëë–
(global-set-key (kbd "M-r") 'backward-paragraph)
(define-key c++-mode-map (kbd "M-r") 'backward-paragraph)

;; C-M-r,f íê¶æ¿¡œ bufferìì“½ ï§¨ ï§£ì„ì“¬æ€¨¼ ëê±¹ìì‘æ¿¡œ ìì” ëë£íë¹€ëë•²ëë–
(global-set-key (kbd "C-M-r") 'beginning-of-buffer)
(global-set-key (kbd "C-M-f") 'end-of-buffer)

;; C-M-j,k íê¶æ¿¡œ forward, backward paragraph ï§ë‚…ì¡Šìì“£ ìë‹”íë»¾íë¹€ëë•²ëë–
(global-set-key (kbd "C-M-j") 'forward-paragraph)
(define-key c++-mode-map (kbd "C-M-j") 'forward-paragraph)
(global-set-key (kbd "C-M-k") 'backward-paragraph)
(define-key c++-mode-map (kbd "C-M-k") 'backward-paragraph)

;; Horizontal <--> Vertical viewç‘œ¼ íë„—æ¹²€íë¹äºŒì‡°ë’— íë¸¿ìë‹”
(defun window-split-toggle ()
  "Toggle between horizontal and vertical split with two windows."
  (interactive)
  (if (> (length (window-list)) 2)
      (error "Can't toggle with more than 2 windows!")
    (let ((func (if (window-full-height-p)
                    #'split-window-vertically
                  #'split-window-horizontally)))
      (delete-other-windows)
      (funcall func)
      (save-selected-window
        (other-window 1)
        (switch-to-buffer (other-buffer))))))

;; Alt + ] íê¶æ¿¡œ horizontal <--> verticalìì“£ íë„—æ¹²€íë¸¯ëë’— íê¶ç‘œ¼ ìê½•ìì ™íë¸³ëë–
(global-set-key (kbd "M-]") 'window-split-toggle)

